import React from 'react'
// import Header from './components/Header'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import PageHome from './components/PageHome.js'
import PageThread from './components/PageThread.js'
import PageNotFound from './components/PageNotFound.js'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path={'/'}>
          <PageHome />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path={'/threads/:threadId'}>
          <PageThread />
        </Route>
        <Route path={'*'}>
          <PageNotFound />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
